description: Updates a detector. After activation, you can only change a detector's ingestion delay and description.

parameters.name: AnomalyDetectorArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the detector to update.

parameters.name: AnomalyDetectorConfig
parameters.description: Contains information about the configuration to which the detector will be updated. AnomalyDetectorFrequency (string) --- The frequency at which the detector analyzes its source data.

nested_params.description: The frequency at which the detector analyzes its source data.
